    "Incorporating Borgmann's ideas, this analysis could also extend to scrutinization of generative AI's prevailing ethical dilemmas-like data privacy breaches, embedded biases, and exacerbating the digital divide-contrasting them with technology's potential to embody authentic human interaction and societal participation.As generative AI becomes more established in language education, it presents much potentiality; yet it is also fraught with concerns that demand careful, informed consideration.",
    "The successful integration of AI will hinge on a balanced appreciation of its capabilities, safeguarding the integrity of learning and cultural richness.",
